a href=\"/best-ethernet-switches\">Ethernet switch</a> comes with the brand’s smart auto-sending features and an unmanaged, plug-and-play design that requires no additional software configurations.","The smart technology feature of this Gigabit Ethernet switch can automatically detect each connection and configure the switch according to what device is connected to the port. This feature also includes network-prevention features that protect against loops, dual images and storm control. This switch has gigabit-speed technology that can handle 10, 100 or 1,000 Mbps. The device also features a total switching capacity of 16 Gbps to ensure fast data transfers and low buffering times.","This Ethernet switch comes with a fanless, quiet design and energy-efficient features that keep the switch cool during operation. The device’s green design supports Energy-Efficient Ethernet and ZyXEL green technology. These allow the device to only use as much energy as needed and to turn unused ports into idle mode to conserve power. The device can also determine how long each cord is and what type of device it is connected to so it can deliver the precise amount of power to each device without wasting energy.","The switch has eight ports on the front of the device with LED indicators next to each. These lights let you know if each port is working so you can troubleshoot issues with individual ports as necessary. Since the lights are positioned on the front of the switch, this eight-port device is easy to mount. The switch also comes with its own mounting hardware so you can attach the switch directly to the wall where needed. You can also set this compact switch directly on your desktop if you prefer. Most other Ethernet switches, like the <a href=\"/d-link-review\">D-Link DGS-1008G</a> and the <a href=\"/tp-link-review\">TP Link TL-SG1005D</a>, have back-facing ports.","While this Buffalo Technology 8-Port Smart Switch was created to help small businesses improve their wired technology, it can also work for your personal needs. The smart technology features and fast gigabit speeds can help with HD streaming, large data transfers and online gaming.","Overall, if you are looking for a reliable Ethernet switch, this product from Buffalo Technology is worth considering. The smart technology features and gigabit speed capabilities make it an ideal choice for those who need to drastically improve their internet speeds across a variety of network components."]},"id":"67873b8c-8154-4368-8070-1a9c73fb4909","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_66486","url":"/buffalo-technology-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"top-ten-reviews-contributor","url":"/author/top-ten-reviews-contributor","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Top Ten Reviews Contributor","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"w5zRTt8zKNM8ERYhxFTX9","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2015-08-07T15:38:49Z","datePublished":"2015-08-07T15:38:49Z","name":"Buffalo Technology BSGS2008","synopsis":"The Buffalo Technology 8 Port Smart Switch offers an inexpensive way to extend a wired business network.","review":{"pros":[""],"cons":[""]},"strapline":"The Buffalo Technology 8 Port Smart Switch offers an inexpensive way to extend a wired business network.","language":"en","dateModified":"2015-08-07T15:38:49Z","id":"kwT3Urx4F5ccdMwvJiun7M","meta":{"title":"Buffalo Technology BSGS2008 Review - Pros, Cons and Verdict","description":"The Buffalo Technology 8-Port Smart Switch offers a cost-effective way to promote a faster business network. Read more about this switch here."},"products":[{"slug":"buffalo-technology-bsgs2008","url":"/product/buffalo-technology-bsgs2008","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T19:28:24Z","name":"Buffalo Technology BSGS2008","dateModified":"2019-04-16T19:28:24Z","id":"yHpDf83VVSHx7JvtSvNcHF","dateImported":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","site":"toptenreviews"}],"dateImported":"2019-04-16T19:28:2